@42 = ~Possibly the oldest of instruments, there are many types and are popular amongst many races for their ability to stir the emotions and establish a beat for dancing.  As well as Humans and Dwarfs, Halforcs, Lizardfolk, Kobolds, trolls, ogres and the more dim-witted giants enjoy simple drum music.~
