@68 = ~Lute~
@69 = ~Elven Lute~
@70 = ~The Lute has a pear-shaped bowl and a distinctive bent neck with frets for fingering. Between four and eight strings stretch between the base of the bowl and the top of the neck. Lutes vary between 30 and 36 inches in length, with the bowl taking up some two thirds of that total. The musician either strums or plucks the strings to produce music.~
// Formely @312, note effect strength +1 missing in @71 (BGEE) compared to @312 (others)
@71 = ~Cassandra's Lute
 'The Lions Courage'
Cassandra started playing the lute when she was 5 years old, by the age of 14 she was a master performer. Her father Tarun Coriades a gifted elven luthier created a special lute for her 16th birthday. Made from mystical woods close to the Lake of Dreams the lute was created to give confidence and courage when played. Cassandra travelled many lands and played in many places with the instrument. Then during a visit to her homeland Evermeet the ship that bore her encountered high seas and the lute was lost overboard. The ship was wrecked on Araska but Cassandra survived only to search for her lute to this day.
   
STATISTICS:

Special: When played the performer gains a sense of confidence and courage. 
THACO: +1 bonus 
Strength increased by 1 
Immunity to fear
5 temporary hit points
Duration: 5 Rounds
Weight: 7
Only Usable by:
  Bard~

